public class Dorm
extends Group

A group of otherwise disconnected Rooms, affiliated only because Students have a greater chance of encountering others in the same dorm than they would otherwise.

Constructor for new Dorm objects.

Parameters:
name - the name of this Dorm, which should be unique across all dorms (though this is not enforced.)
femaleOnly - is this dorm intended to allow only female occupants?
freshmanOnly - is this dorm intended to allow only freshman occupants?
numRooms - the number of rooms in the dorm.
